  "detailed_description": "<h1>NOTE FROM THE DEVELOPER</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was created independently with a focus on atmosphere and psychological tension. Player feedback helps shape future updates and future games — every project will grow and improve with the community.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How far would you go to pass… the assessment?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up alone in a locked room.<br>Questions must be answered.<br>Choices must be made.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision is watched.<br>Every mistake has consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not just a test...<br>It’s a test of fear, pressure, and control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you stay calm long enough to survive the assessment?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How far would you go to pass… the assessment?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up alone in a locked room.<br>Questions must be answered.<br>Choices must be made.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision is watched.<br>Every mistake has consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not just a test...<br>It’s a test of fear, pressure, and control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you stay calm long enough to survive the assessment?</p>",
